OL,3,CGrandmother spared jail after
OL,4,C'shameful' family day out at riots
OL,6,FA judge told a grandmother she should
OL,7,Fbe "deeply ashamed of her behaviour"
OL,8,Fafter going to a riot with her
OL,9,Fdaughter and baby grandson in a pram.
OL,11,FFootage captured Vanessa Smith, 42 and
OL,12,Fher 21-year-old daughter, with her 20-
OL,13,Fmonth old son in a pram, throwing
OL,14,Fwater at a police officer outside a
OL,15,Fhotel housing asylum seekers in Newton
OL,16,FHeath in Manchester July.
OL,18,FThe court heard how the three
OL,19,Fgenerations of the Smith family ended
OL,20,Fup among around the 50-70 strong crowd
OL,21,Fthat had gathered outside the hotel.
