OL,3,CGrandmother spared jail after
OL,4,C'shameful' family day out at riots
OL,6,FJudge Patrick Field KC who had
OL,7,Fsentenced her granddaughter,
OL,8,Fdescribing Nevey Smith's actions as
OL,9,F"disturbing" and labelling her
OL,10,F"misguided, naive and immature".
OL,12,FHe said: "It's a disturbing feature
OL,13,Fthat you chose to join it (the riot)
OL,14,Fwith your child with you. It's a
OL,15,Fdisturbing part of this case. What
OL,16,Fwere you thinking?"
OL,18,FThe judge also told the single mum
OL,19,Fthat she had a "lot to learn" and
OL,20,F"quite a lot of growing up to do".
