OL,3,CGrandmother spared jail after
OL,4,C'shameful' family day out at riots
OL,6,FShe was handed a community order and
OL,7,Fmade to attend reviews at a women's
OL,8,Fproblem-solving court, and carry out
OL,9,F100 hours of unpaid work.
OL,11,FThe same judge was in court to
OL,12,Fsentence grandmother Vanessa Smith, a
OL,13,Fmum-of-three with two other children
OL,14,Faged 16 and 11, who handed herself in
OL,15,Fto police and pleaded guilty to
OL,16,Fviolent disorder.
OL,18,FDuring the disorder, a bus was
OL,19,Fattacked and an asylum seeker being
OL,20,Fescorted into the hotel was injured by
OL,21,Fflying glass.
