OL,3,CGrandmother spared jail after
OL,4,C'shameful' family day out at riots
OL,6,FThe prosecution told how Vanessa Smith
OL,7,Fwas seen as part of the group and
OL,8,Fthrew liquid towards police officers.
OL,10,FJudge Field told her that she had been
OL,11,F'wholly misguided' in her involvement
OL,12,Fin the mob and the court heard how she
OL,13,Fhad suffered the loss of her
OL,14,Femployment at a Failsworth cafe as a
OL,15,Fresult.
