OL,3,CGrandmother spared jail after
OL,4,C'shameful' family day out at riots
OL,6,FVanessa Smith, of Farnborough Road in
OL,7,FFailsworth, was sentenced to an 18
OL,8,Fmonth community order, 100 hours of
OL,9,Funpaid work, 15 rehabilitation
OL,10,Factivity days, and ordered to make a
OL,11,Fpayment of #150 to the cost of
OL,12,Fproceedings.
OL,14,FThe judge accepted the defence's
OL,15,Fsubmission that it was an 'isolated
OL,16,Fincident and out of character', with
OL,17,Fthe throwing of water being the height
OL,18,Fof her contribution to the day's chaos.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
