OL,3,CGrandmother spared jail after
OL,4,C'shameful' family day out at riots
OL,6,FBut he called her behaviour 'mistaken,
OL,7,Fill-advised', and' completely
OL,8,Funacceptable'.
OL,10,F"You should be duly ashamed,
OL,11,Fparticularly as there were children
OL,12,Fpresent - your grandson was present.
OL,13,FI'm confident that what we've just
OL,14,Fseen and heard about is not the
OL,15,Fexample you would want to hold up for
OL,16,Fyour children and grandchildren,"
OL,17,Fadded the judge.
