OL,3,CGrandmother spared jail after
OL,4,C'shameful' family day out at riots
OL,6,FVanessa Smith sighed as she was spared
OL,7,Fjail, as Judge Field said: "You've
OL,8,Freceived a merciful sentence, don't
OL,9,Flet me down."
OL,11,FThe judge told Smith that if she
OL,12,Fbreached the order, she'd be returned
OL,13,Fto court.
OL,15,F"I don't forget a case or a face", he
OL,16,Ftold her... "and if you return to
OL,17,Fcourt you can be punished for that
OL,18,Fbreach."
